<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc0524051-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s18111"><num value="18111">§ 18111.</num><heading> Definitions</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Unless specifically provided for otherwise, the definitions contained in <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s300gg–91">section 300gg–91 of this title</ref> shall apply with respect to this title.<ref class="footnoteRef" idref="fn004342">1</ref><note type="footnote" id="fn004342"><num>1</num> See References in Text note below.</note></p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc0524052-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/111/148/tI/s1551">Pub. L. 111–148, title I, § 1551</ref>, <date date="2010-03-23">Mar. 23, 2010</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/124/258">124 Stat. 258</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
